Package ki306.yarema.lab4.models

Interface CommanderEquipment

All Known Implementing Classes:
CommanderGasMask
public interface CommanderEquipment
The CommanderEquipment interface represents the equipment used by the commander. All classes that implement this interface must provide methods for getting the type of equipment and sending an SOS signal.
